goals.active: The Ringmaster is gathering new recruits.
goals.complete: Along with the other recruits, I met with the Ringmaster in the forest. It turned out to be a trap. The Ringmaster wanted to test the effects of the Floating Grizwhirl. It hypnotized the recruits. I had to beat them back to their senses. The Ringmaster is going to use the Floating Grizwhirl to hypnotize the audience at the next big show in Divinity's Reach. I have to stop him.
